{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket: message event","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\"><code>send()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.message_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code>message</code>&nbsp;事件会在&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;接收到新消息时被触发。</p>\n\n<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">起泡（Bubbles）</th>\n   <td>不</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可取消</th>\n   <td>不</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">接口</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">事件处理程序属性</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\" title=\"onmessage\"><code>onmessage</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">// 创建一个 WebSocket 连接\nconst socket = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:8080');\n\n// 监听消息\nsocket.addEventListener('message', function (event) {\n    console.log('Message from server ', event.data);\n});</pre>\n\n\n\n<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th>规范</th>\n   <th>状态</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#event-message\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">WebSocket message</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\">WebSocket: close event</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\">WebSocket: error event</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\">WebSocket: open event</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\">Writing WebSocket client applications</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"message 事件会在 WebSocket 接收到新消息时被触发。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket: message event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSocket : évènement message","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket: message イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/websocket/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/websocket/message_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","title":"WebSocket"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event","title":"WebSocket: message event"}],"pageTitle":"WebSocket: message event - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}